  <Content>Loures Soccer Event
 
Become pioneers in the fastest growing sport in Temuair, Suomi Soccer!
 
Suomi Soccer is an organized sporting event, wherein two teams must strategically compete against each other. The object of the game is to successfully drag an item to the opposing team's threshold (scoring a point). Thus, every participant must carry enough weight in their inventory to the extent that they cannot actually pick up the game item. A Soccer Ball shall be used in this tournament.
 
